message.1
	Welcome to Adventure: 6 `STRANGE ODYSSEY` by Scott Adams.\nDedicated to the Novaks.\n
message.2
	Nothing happens
message.3
	OK
message.4
	Pressure gauge says
message.5
	moves till suit air expended. Air outside suit is
message.6
	The outside has a pressure gauge & a connecter for a hose.
message.7
	breathable.
message.8
	not
message.9
	Stale air is
message.10
	It is
message.11
	My air ran out!
message.12
	Some GAS comes out of the hose for awhile then stops.
message.13
	\nPhaser is set on:
message.14
	DESTROY!
message.15
	stun.
message.16
	`TO STUN` or `TO DESTROY` ?
message.17
	(use 2 words)
message.18
	\nMy suit popped open!
message.19
	Warning light says: `POWER CRYSTAL DAMAGED`
message.20
	Blue button marked `BLAST OFF` & a unmarked red button
message.21
	Console replies: `INSUFFICIENT POWER`
message.22
	Alien script covers it
message.23
	I fire the Phaser,
message.24
	I destroyed it!
message.25
	Air is getting stale! Read gauge!
message.26
	won't budge!
message.27
	I see nothing special.
message.28
	Its some sort of force field.
message.29
	I ruined the ship!
message.30
	Either I missed or beam was absorbed without visible effect!
message.31
	Its empty.
message.32
	Charge left registers:
message.33
	It seems to be as far
message.34
	out
message.35
	in
message.36
	as it will go.
message.37
	Odd it only required very little force
message.38
	for it to break off in my hand with a\nCRYSTALLINE snap!
message.39
	HOW?
message.40
	The plastic GLOWED briefly
message.41
	times.
message.42
	for it to shatter!
message.43
	I feel strangely disoriented for a moment!
message.44
	to slide
message.45
	Ice Hound attacks me unexpectidly!
message.46
	It woke up!
message.47
	I found nothing
message.48
	We're drifting in space!
message.49
	I see: a black button, a white button, a hose.
message.50
	Hose rips out
message.51
	Tight fit!
message.52
	Lift off!! After a brief flight we arrive...
message.53
	The Ice Hound burrows off...
message.54
	Ice fills back in around me as I dig my way in. The\npick broke but I made it!
message.55
	Ice is very smooth & hard!
message.56
	I slide back down.
message.57
	I don't know where to look
message.58
	Try: `SHOOT SOMETHING`
message.59
	Say again & use a color
message.60
	There's writing there
message.61
	I can't do that
message.62
	Whooosh!
message.63
	The gravity here is very
message.64
	strong.
message.65
	weak.
message.66
	Its stuck.
message.67
	I'm SQUASHED!
message.68
	The power crystal was in the shape of a thin rod.
message.69
	I feel LIGHT HEADED!
message.70
	It floats!
message.71
	A gentle touch will work wonders!
message.72
	It should fit. It has a large buckle.
message.73
	Painting is of an Alien twisting a buckle on a belt.
message.74
	Wiring behind plastic shorts & I'm electrocuted!
message.75
	I see a picture of an ALIEN TENTACLE.
message.76
	Wonderful. It ATE me!
message.77
	It is of an alien being.
message.78
	Its wearing only a strange belt!
message.79
	Watch it! Its known to spit molten DIAMONDS!
message.80
	There's a box on it with a yellow button.
message.81
	I just see shades of black, it makes my eyes swim!
message.82
	I think its broken!
message.83
	I found something.
message.84
	Ouch!
message.85
	its stunned!
message.86
	The metal helped!
message.87
